sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,TrustyAISvc: Flow 1: TrustyAI Service Payload Processing
        participant Client as External Client
        participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant RBAC1 as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP TLS
        participant TrustyAISvc as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
        participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh/KServe<br/>InferenceService

        Client->>Router: HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>External auth
        Router->>RBAC1: HTTPS/8443 (TLS reencrypt)<br/>SAR enforcement
        RBAC1->>TrustyAISvc: HTTP/8080 (localhost)<br/>No auth
        ModelMesh->>RBAC1: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>HTTPS/8443 (serving cert)<br/>MM_PAYLOAD_PROCESSORS env
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over User,OCI: Flow 2: LMEvalJob Execution
        participant User as User
        participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
        participant LMESCtrl as LMES Controller
        participant EvalPod as Evaluation Pod
        participant Driver as ta-lmes-driver<br/>18080/TCP localhost
        participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

        User->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>HTTPS/6443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Bearer token
        K8sAPI-->>LMESCtrl: Reconcile event
        LMESCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create eval Pod<br/>HTTPS/6443 (SA token)
        Note over EvalPod: Init container copies<br/>driver binary
        EvalPod->>Driver: Start driver process
        Driver->>S3: Download assets (if offline)<br/>HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>AWS IAM credentials
        S3-->>Driver: Evaluation assets
        Driver->>Driver: Run lm-evaluation-harness
        LMESCtrl->>Driver: GET /GetStatus<br/>HTTP/18080 (pod exec)
        Driver-->>LMESCtrl: Job progress/status
        Driver->>OCI: Upload results (if configured)<br/>HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Basic auth / Docker config
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over GORCHCtrl,Detector: Flow 3: Guardrails Orchestrator Auto-Discovery
        participant GORCHCtrl as GORCH Controller
        participant InfSvc as InferenceServices
        participant DetectorSvc as Detector Services
        participant OrchestratorPod as Orchestrator Pod
        participant Detector as Detector Endpoint

        GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: List InferenceServices<br/>HTTPS/6443 (SA token)
        K8sAPI-->>GORCHCtrl: InferenceService list
        GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: List Services by label<br/>HTTPS/6443 (SA token)
        K8sAPI-->>GORCHCtrl: Detector service list
        GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMaps<br/>(orchestrator config)
        OrchestratorPod->>InfSvc: Forward inference request<br/>HTTPS/HTTP (TLS if detected)
        OrchestratorPod->>Detector: Check content safety<br/>HTTPS/HTTP (TLS if detected)
    end

    rect rgb(248, 240, 255)
        Note over EHClient,MLFlowSvc: Flow 4: EvalHub Evaluation and Monitoring
        participant EHClient as Client
        participant EHRouter as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant EvalHubSvc as EvalHub Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
        participant DB as PostgreSQL/SQLite<br/>5432/TCP
        participant MLFlowSvc as MLFlow Tracking<br/>HTTPS
        participant JobReconciler as Job Failure<br/>Reconciler

        EHClient->>EHRouter: HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>External auth
        EHRouter->>EvalHubSvc: HTTPS/8443 (TLS reencrypt)<br/>SAR (X-Tenant scoped)
        EvalHubSvc->>DB: Query/Store data<br/>5432/TCP (TLS if configured)<br/>DB credentials
        EvalHubSvc->>MLFlowSvc: Experiment tracking<br/>HTTPS (TLS service CA)<br/>Projected SA token
        JobReconciler->>EvalHubSvc: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}/events<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Operator SA token
    end
